2012年1月28日，时任柳州市副市长王柳平与相关部门负责人于下午去往柳西水厂检查。<ref name="RB29-6">{{cite news| url=http://www.lznews.gov.cn:9999/epaper/lzrb/html/2012/01/29/02/02_47.htm| title=确保按计划完成任务| work=柳州日报| date=2012-01-29| accessdate=2012-02-10| author=郑燕军| location=柳州| pages=2| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121209104135/http://www.lznews.gov.cn:9999/epaper/lzrb/html/2012/01/29/02/02_47.htm| archivedate=2012-12-09}}</ref>时任柳州市威立雅水务公司副总黄永强表示，该公司有能力将镉超标2倍的原水处理为合格自来水。<ref name="NG29-2">{{cite news| url=http://epaper.gxnews.com.cn/ngjb/html/2012-01/29/content_1957797.htm| title=绝不允许污染物进入城市供水管网| work=南国今报| date=2012-01-29| accessdate=2012-02-01| author=王小丁| location=柳州| pages=2| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130101191612/http://epaper.gxnews.com.cn/ngjb/html/2012-01/29/content_1957797.htm| archivedate=2013-01-01| df=}}</ref><ref name="RB29-7">{{cite news| url=http://www.lznews.gov.cn:9999/epaper/lzrb/html/2012/01/29/03/03_48.htm| title=保证自来水都是合格的水| work=柳州日报| date=2012-01-29| accessdate=2012-02-10| author=张晓军| location=柳州| pages=3| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023351/http://www.lznews.gov.cn:9999/epaper/lzrb/html/2012/01/29/03/03_48.htm| archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref>

